	<h1 class="title">全城都是设计展，要如何让人注意到你？｜米兰设计周</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">宁卉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-14 12:15:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25460/medium/25460.jpg?1460599305" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


